data.description: Step into this spacious 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom home in Huntwyck Village. As you pull into the driveway you can see the 2 car garage, with an electronic garage door, and a charming courtyard leading to the front door. This floorplan layout provides lots of privacy. Through the front door you enter into the living area that is large enough to fit a full dining table, along with extra flex space for a breakfast nook, office nook or play area. The living area includes a wood burning fireplace, a large window overlooking the backyard and tons of natural light. To the left is the galley kitchen, with room for another seating area or a mudroom area leading to the interior garage entrance. The washer and dryer hookups are located in the garage. Back through the living area, to the right, is the bedrooms and bathrooms. The primary bedroom includes a large en suite full bathroom and walk-in closet. Each of the windows, soffits and fascia were replaced in February 2023 by Window World and have a transferable lifetime warranty. The roof was replaced in 2022. The A/C is only 4 years old, replaced in 2019. The home also includes installed security cameras and exterior color-changing flood lights. The neighborhood does have an HOA. Members get to enjoy the community in-ground pool and four separate playgrounds / park areas. Schedule an appointment to see it in person.
